#   The tree is the undeniable center of that world. We reveal beauty at
#   every scale: campus → courtyard → trunk → canopy → roots.
#   No students yet. The audience falls in love with what they cannot see.
#
# Shot order: wide → closer → closer → detail → back to wide with contrast.
# Reference: the monolith reveal, 2001: A Space Odyssey.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

